                                <h3 class="heading post-category">Category
                                    Name</h3>
                                <h1 class="title post-title">The "I'll Pour Another IPA" Box$</h1>
                                <p class="post-excerpt">This IPA selection will have all beer drinkers saying "I'll Pour
                                    Another". With a selection of 4 different IPA's
                                    from around the World. A New England IPA with floral and spice notes. A West Coast
