                            <div class="column is-12 post-img">
                                <img src="./pic/Microbrew-Beer-Bucket-Gift-Basket-3-Beers_large.jpg"
                                    alt="Featured Image">
                            </div>
                            <div class="column is-12 featured-content">
                                <h3 class="heading post-category">Category
                                    Name</h3>
                                <h1 class="title post-title">The "Aielmans Ale" Box</h1>
                                <p class="post-excerpt">The Aielmans Ale's, meant to quench your thirst in even the
                                    driest deserts. These 5 Ale's range from light to dark, from Pale Ale's to Brown.
                                    This Box comes with a pair of British Style Imperial Pint Glasses and a 10% off
                                    discount card to Bad Daddys Burger Bar.</p>
                                <br>
                                <a href="#" class="button
                                    has-background-grey
                                    has-text-success-light">Subscribe</a>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
